# init(contentsOf:)

**Initializer**

Initializes a filter generator object with the contents of a filter generator file.

## Declaration

```swift
init?(contentsOf aURL: URL)
```

## Parameters

- **aURL**: The location of a filter generator file.

## Return Value

The initialized [doc://com.apple.coreimage/documentation/CoreImage/CIFilterGenerator] object. Returns `nil` if the file can’t be read.
